{"tid":631940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高薪低能] 申訴專員斥水務署監管爆水管力度不足","createTime":"2018-04-17T02:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T09:01:15.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"323f201f0febaad874c0dab6d88fe43f5b51e8d7","tid":631940,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"申訴專員公署批評，水務署監管爆水管力度不足。<br />\n<br />\n公署就政府水管維修進行主動調查發現，本港水管滲漏比率超過15%，明顯落後於新加坡的5%，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等同每年浪費多約5.3億元的食水</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n公署認為，水務署沒有重點監察重覆爆水管個案，對因工程破壞水管的民事索償力度亦不足，要求水務署加強監察，降低水管滲漏比率。"},{"pid":"b30f5696de30d8a6b74578a661727fe76d09b2d2","tid":631940,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"管監不力得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94353cff656540865b7642eab8e30c02b0426580","tid":631940,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30f5696de30d8a6b74578a661727fe76d09b2d2","tid":631940,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"管監不力得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"監管"},{"pid":"93a3de65732f7275dcf8fcc19244b7d969eae936","tid":631940,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"好似永遠都剩係見到申訴專員公署話人呢樣錯嗰樣不足<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個去查申訴專員公署? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8625aa4a724d9eddb970c4682a6093a78a33899d","tid":631940,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8057c5ba1298486e70bb05f2ef825c487949634d","tid":631940,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94353cff656540865b7642eab8e30c02b0426580","tid":631940,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30f5696de30d8a6b74578a661727fe76d09b2d2","ti